              <td>
                <p><b>No implementation needed - </b>UK law<authorialNote marker="3"><p> Here and elsewhere in this table references to “UK law” include references to rules contained in the PRA rulebook.</p></authorialNote> already provides for this </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Not applicable</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
