              <td>
                <p>Regulation 35 of the Capital Requirements (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2018 – which amends regulation 2 of the Capital Requirements (Capital Buffers and Macro-prudential Measures) Regulations 2014</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 13</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Capital Buffers 2 </p>
              </td>
