              <td>
                <p>Regulations 35 and 60 of the Capital Requirements (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2018 – which amends regulation 2 and inserts new Part 5A into the Capital Requirements (Capital Buffers and Macro-prudential Measures) Regulations 2014 </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulations 13 and 19</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
              </td>
            </tr>
